d and outbound fax process  Action Required  As stated in the informational document received faxes will appear in a fax mailbox corresponding to each fax number  It is recommended the departmental secretary and an alternate have access to manage your departmental fax mailbox  Please send email to Help vmi edu submitting at least two names from your department along with your fax number  If you do not know if your fax will be replaced with a new Ricoh MFP  please access this link http www vmi edu printprogram and find your printer number on the printer map  Then find your printer number on the printer legend which will provide you with information about the status    VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 